items.preText: vivek: "how's mushifiquir ? still struggling?" -- Yes sir. The heat can drain the body and cause the cramps.
items.text: back of a length on off, and flicked off his pads to the vacant square-leg region
items.shortText: Mohammad Nawaz to Mahmudullah, 1 run

items.text: full on leg stump, and pushed with the angled bat to midwicket. A wild throw to the bowler almost makes it go for an overthrow, but mid off was backing up
items.shortText: Mohammad Nawaz to Mushfiqur Rahim, 1 run

items.text: good length outside off, and he cuts the ball off the back foot. But the shot is bottom-edged onto the ground and straight into Sarfraz's gloves
items.shortText: Mohammad Nawaz to Mahmudullah, no run

items.text: full just outside off, and tapped off the front foot to cover. Seven off the over
items.shortText: Mohammad Nawaz to Mahmudullah, no run

items.preText: Mahneel Musa: "The first 10 bowls of every Mahmudullah innings is important. If he survives, get set for a big knock"
items.text: length ball outside off, and the legbreak takes it away from the batsman. He mistimes the cut to point
items.shortText: Shadab Khan to Mushfiqur Rahim, no run

items.text: full toss outside off, and Mushfiqur's eyes light up. Swings across the line, and the ball lands in no man's land! Long on was far away
items.shortText: Shadab Khan to Mushfiqur Rahim, 2 runs

items.text: full toss on off stump, and driven down the ground to long on
items.shortText: Shadab Khan to Mushfiqur Rahim, 1 run

items.text: good length on off, and skidding through. Fended off the back foot to cover
items.shortText: Shadab Khan to Mahmudullah, no run

items.text: good length outside off, and spinning into the batsman. Cut past point to the fielder in the deep
items.shortText: Shadab Khan to Mahmudullah, 1 run

items.text: good length outside off, and he pulls this off the back foot to deep midwicket
items.shortText: Shadab Khan to Mushfiqur Rahim, 1 run

items.text: full on middle stump, and comfortably whipped off his pads to deep backward square. Runs back fast for the second run, and the throw from the deep is pretty weak
items.shortText: Shaheen Shah Afridi to Mushfiqur Rahim, 2 runs

items.text: full just outside off stump, and he drives through the ball's line to extra cover for a walking single
items.shortText: Shaheen Shah Afridi to Mushfiqur Rahim, 1 run

items.preText: Sonal Trivedi: "Mushi in 90's.... Hope he won't be Nervous. BD need him till end of inning" -- six away from his second hundred of the Asia Cup
items.text: back of a length outside off, and tapped off the back foot to point with the angled bat
items.shortText: Shaheen Shah Afridi to Mahmudullah, no run

items.text: full on off stump, and his leg-side whip takes a leading edge to Imam at wide cover
items.shortText: Shaheen Shah Afridi to Mahmudullah, 2 runs

items.text: good length on off, and tapped off the front foot to mid on. The fielder - Shadab - fails to pick up the ball, and therefore the batsman complete a comfortable single. Could've been dangerous otherwise
items.shortText: Shaheen Shah Afridi to Mahmudullah, 1 run

items.text: yorker on leg stump, but he manages to wedge this away to the leg side.
items.postText: Ten overs to go, and time for Karthik to return for the final stages of the innings. Predictions on Bangladesh's final score?
items.shortText: Shaheen Shah Afridi to Mushfiqur Rahim, no run

items.preText: Thanks, Sreshth. This is extremely interesting now. Two quality players out there, but only five wickets in hand, and an extra fielder on the boundary. Here's Shadab.
items.text: tossed up full on off stump, clipped to long-on
items.shortText: Shadab Khan to Mahmudullah, 1 run

items.text: tossed up slow, wide of off stump, swept along the ground to the left of deep midwicket
items.shortText: Shadab Khan to Mushfiqur Rahim, 1 run

items.text: googly, a touch short, stabbed to cover point. Interesting field - cover point is in the circle and there's a deep extra-cover back. Usually it's the other way round
items.shortText: Shadab Khan to Mahmudullah, no run

items.text: flatter, front of the hand. Skids through close to off stump, no turn, and Mahmudullah, looking to punch to deep extra cover, ends up stabbing it back to the bowler
items.shortText: Shadab Khan to Mahmudullah, no run

items.text: another googly, turns in towards off stump as Mahmudullah looks to make room. Punched to cover point
items.shortText: Shadab Khan to Mahmudullah, no run

items.text: tossed up much slower on off stump and Mahmudullah, tied down by those dot balls, looks for the slog-sweep to release the pressure. Ends up top-edging it loopily to the right of the keeper
items.shortText: Shadab Khan to Mahmudullah, 3 runs

items.text: full, angling into the pads, clipped to long leg
items.shortText: Shaheen Shah Afridi to Mahmudullah, 1 run

items.text: ooh, edged past the diving keeper. Nicely bowled, back of a length and it nips away off the seam. Looks to dab it down to third man, ends up edging it much finer than intended, but gets four runs for it
items.shortText: Shaheen Shah Afridi to Mushfiqur Rahim, FOUR runs

items.text: and he'll stay there for now. Full, into the blockhole on off stump. Jabbed back to the bowler
items.shortText: Shaheen Shah Afridi to Mushfiqur Rahim, no run
